 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/853/how-to-jump-to-urgent-workspace/?answer=858#post-id-858</link><description>You can do that using the "urgent" criteria:

    bindsym $mod+x [urgent=latest] focus</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Dec 2012 16:39:50 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/853/how-to-jump-to-urgent-workspace/?answer=858#post-id-858</guid></item><item><title>Comment by psamim for &lt;p&gt;You can do that using the "urgent" criteria:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;bindsym $mod+x [urgent=latest] focus
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
